    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="J1737">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Rearrange a "Wife's" affection!</l>
                    <l>When they dislocate my Brain!</l>
                    <l>Amputate my freckled Bosom!</l>
                    <l>Make me bearded like a man!</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Blush, my spirit, in thy Fastness --</l>
                    <l>Blush, my unacknowledged clay --</l>
                    <l>Seven years of troth have taught thee</l>
                    <l>More than Wifehood ever may!</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Love that never leaped its socket --</l>
                    <l>Trust entrenched in narrow pain --</l>
                    <l>Constancy thro' fire -- awarded --</l>
                    <l>Anguish -- bare of anodyne!</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Burden -- borne so far triumphant --</l>
                    <l>None suspect me of the crown,</l>
                    <l>For I wear the "Thorns" till Sunset --</l>
                    <l>Then -- my Diadem put on.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Big my Secret but it's bandaged --</l>
                    <l>It will never get away</l>
                    <l>Till the Day its Weary Keeper</l>
                    <l>Leads it through the Grave to thee.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
